Event:     E_GOT_HIT

Called:    Whenever an object received a hit in fight.

Usage:     Add an event (see add_event), create an event handling function, 
           that will be called if the event occurs:
	   void function(object o, object ao, int damage, int slot,
                         object w) { ... }

Arguments: object o    - the object that made the hit
	   object ao   - the object that has been hit
           int damage  - the damage that has been inflicted
           int slot    - the slot that has been hit
           object w    - the weapon object that caused the hit (0 if no weapon)
